Class CityResources

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.CityResources
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class CityResources
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Represents the resources and the parameters of the city. An ephemeral resource is reset at each step thanks to getVat().
    See Also:
